Title: Fallen (1)
Plot: While searching for the Lost City of the Ancients on a distant planet, SG-1 is stunned to find Daniel Jackson alive and in human form but stripped of his memory.  O'Neill convinces Daniel to return with them to the SGC, where he is reinstated for a daring mission to destroy Anubis' powerful new super-weapon!
GuestStars: Corin Nemec, George Touliatos, Kevan Ohtsji, Eric Breker, Raahul Singh, Jonathan Newmarch, Mary-Jane Baker
